{"tid":2510371,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩連奴下一站：華倫西亞","createTime":"2021-04-30T06:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T06:24:42.000Z","uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8c9a31af865fe9e6d5f383917187faa7167e654c","tid":2510371,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:22:10.000Z","msg":"摩連奴突然被熱刺解僱之後，一直都沒有下一步消息，西班牙傳媒爆料指華倫西亞老闆親自點名，準備同摩帥在西班牙見面，<br />\n<br />\n西媒指華倫西亞大老闆對寸王情有獨鍾，摩連奴離開英超之後，已直接點名要他執教，同時爆料指華西高層同寸王的經理人已開始商談，有華倫高層承認摩連奴出任主帥基本上已拍板，呢兩日摩連奴亦會親自飛到西班牙與球會大老闆會面。<br />\n<br />\n華倫西亞今季戰績不佳，31場只得35分排名西甲第14位，高層對主帥查維加西亞十分不滿意，只是一直未找到理想人選。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.sportinglife.com/images/news/945x532/5acdf3df-7a59-4d36-8572-d0e0d609944b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sportinglife.com%2Fimages%2Fnews%2F945x532%2F5acdf3df-7a59-4d36-8572-d0e0d609944b.jpg&h=7c31e041&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"596086addc45d7b0140315b896adf021413cba7c","tid":2510371,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96abdca538d4f5d6a27b7778fb373ac8bef14953","tid":2510371,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:24:08.000Z","msg":"教國家隊好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d035830db57e2ee1b2fef21f3bdb6a12cac6c4","tid":2510371,"uid":1202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:24:11.000Z","msg":"淪落到教華倫西亞 抵死啦 不思進取"},{"pid":"cabda4ed94ee3b6d3d665d3a936ceb7b9cffdc8d","tid":2510371,"uid":100766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:24:42.000Z","msg":"屌喇星<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}